original_title: Super Size Me! 11: Breed Em Big
overview: Who says size doesn’t matter? Not this bunch of crazily horny bastards, that’s for fuckin’ sure; as the biggest boys in town get together to help satisfy another collection of inch-obsessed beauties. Be it Hector Augusti’s king-sized black salami or Jace Reed’s hole-destroying weapon of ass-destruction, the poor twinks in this feature never really stand a chance. Impaled to the max, but oh so fuckin’ happy with it, you can be sure that the likes of Ray Mannix, Tony Conrad and Xavier Sibley are never, ever gonna be the same again!
title: Super Size Me! 11: Breed Em Big
